Welcome to SHOUTT

SHOUTT is a social news service for Trinidad & Tobago for users to share their news of happenings around Trinidad. Users can geolocate stories and track them by time as well.

Here's how it looks:
Video: http://vimeo.com/12380719
Pictures: http://bit.ly/shoutt



Installation Instructions
--------------------------------

These instructions are application specific. They assume you've already configured your local server properly.

1. Import the db > schema.sql file into mysql as a new database

2. Edit the system > application > config > database.php.sample to suit your specifications, then rename the file to "database.php" (removing the ".sample" at the end)

And you're done.

